markets.title: Will annual **nominal U.S. GDP growth** be above 7.5% in 2022?
markets.rules_primary: If U.S. nominal GDP growth in 2022 is above 7.5% according to the BEA, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
The market will always close at 8:25 AM ET on January 26, 2023. The data is expected to be released at 8:30 AM ET on that date.

Please see the Rulebook's Instructions section on how to calculate the Underlying. In short, go to the Source Agency link, click on the Edit Graph button and change "Units" to "Percent Change from a Year Ago".
